{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"56886ce6-6e3a-5a28-a5bb-8a990105ffcc","excerpt":"結緣貼紙 最近參加 Con 拿到的貼紙庫存，我把它們 po 在社群網站上要和大家結緣。 首位要結緣的朋友是想拿這張參加 MOPCON 從  Chatbot.tw  攤位 擼 回來的 LINE 貼紙。 莎莉 LGTM LGTM 到底是什麼意思呢？Google 了一下才知道原來是 GitHub…","html":"<h3>結緣貼紙</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/7b0d7/github-slang-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"github slang 0\"\n        title=\"github slang 0\"\n        src=\"/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/55071/github-slang-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/493b1/github-slang-0.jpg 163w,\n/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/17f95/github-slang-0.jpg 325w,\n/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/55071/github-slang-0.jpg 650w,\n/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/4194c/github-slang-0.jpg 975w,\n/static/8b345cba60a43d3f41597e1bf52c119e/7b0d7/github-slang-0.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>最近參加 Con 拿到的貼紙庫存，我把它們 po 在社群網站上要和大家結緣。</p>\n<p>首位要結緣的朋友是想拿這張參加 MOPCON 從 <a href=\"http://chatbot.tw\">Chatbot.tw</a> 攤位<del>擼</del>回來的 LINE 貼紙。</p>\n<h3>莎莉 LGTM</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/7b0d7/github-slang-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"github slang 1\"\n        title=\"github slang 1\"\n        src=\"/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/55071/github-slang-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/493b1/github-slang-1.jpg 163w,\n/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/17f95/github-slang-1.jpg 325w,\n/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/55071/github-slang-1.jpg 650w,\n/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/4194c/github-slang-1.jpg 975w,\n/static/5c35287616f8ba0093da20d1f5a7fc5e/7b0d7/github-slang-1.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>LGTM 到底是什麼意思呢？Google 了一下才知道原來是 GitHub 上常用的縮寫啊！</p>\n<p>整理一下網路上找到的常用縮寫：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>LGTM</strong>: Looks Good To Me.</li>\n<li><strong>SGTM</strong>: Sounds Goood To Me.</li>\n<li><strong>PTAL</strong>: Please Take A Look.</li>\n<li><strong>WIP</strong>: Work In Progress.</li>\n<li><strong>TL;DR</strong>: Too Long; Don’t Read.</li>\n<li><strong>TBD</strong>: To Be Done(or Defined/Discussed/Decided/Determined).</li>\n<li><strong>TBR</strong>: To Be Reviewed.</li>\n<li><strong>PR</strong>: Pull Request</li>\n<li><strong>ACK</strong>: Acknowledgement, i.e. agreed/accepted change</li>\n<li><strong>NACK/NAK</strong>: Negative Acknowledgement, i.e. disagree with change and/or concept</li>\n<li><strong>RFC</strong>: Request For Comments, i.e. I think this is a good idea, lets discuss</li>\n<li><strong>AFAIK/AFAICT</strong>: As Far As I Know / Can Tell</li>\n<li><strong>IIRC</strong>: If I Recall Correctly</li>\n<li><strong>IANAL</strong>: “I Am Not A Lawyer”, but I smell licensing issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上，還有哪些常用縮寫呢？知道請<a href=\"mailto:hello@p3t.lu\">告訴我</a>。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>參考資料來源：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://farer.org/2017/03/01/code-review-acronyms/\">LGTM? 那些迷之缩写</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/what-do-cryptic-github-comments-mean-9c1912bcc0a4/\">What do cryptic Github comments mean?</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"TL;DR? LGTM? 什麼意思？","date":"October 26, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/github-slang/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/modify-koko-id/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"國泰世華 KOKO ID 變更方法"}},"next":null}}